<subSubSection box="[151,1419,1266,1293]" pageId="21" pageNumber="394" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1436,1230,1365]" box="[151,1419,1266,1293]" pageId="21" pageNumber="394">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,305,1266,1292]" pageId="21" pageNumber="394">Distribution.</emphasis>
The species is reported in 
<collectingCountry box="[567,639,1266,1292]" name="Cyprus" pageId="21" pageNumber="394">Cyprus</collectingCountry>
for the first time. In Vasiliko Bay, it is considered as a rare species (FI: 2.38 %).
</paragraph>
