<quantity box="[583,637,1302,1329]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" pageId="21" pageNumber="394" unit="m" value="35.0">35 m</quantity>
depth in muddy sand substrate with 6.265 % organic matter. The station was in “moderate” ecological status according to the Bentix Index.
</paragraph>
